# Refresh OIDC provider metadata every 6 hours.
# Install by running: crontab -e
# Adjust the path to match your deployment root.
#
# This keeps authorization_endpoint, token_endpoint, jwks_uri, and
# end_session_endpoint current without requiring manual admin action.
# The job validates that the fetched issuer still matches the configured
# value before writing any updates.
#
# 0 */6 * * *  cd /var/www/campfire && bin/rails runner "Identity::RefreshMetadataJob.perform_now" >> log/identity_refresh.log 2>&1
#
# Alternatively, if you use systemd timers, create a .timer unit that
# calls the same rails runner command.
